	Customers have realtime access to their energy information via the Internet from their computer or smartphone
	</h2>
      <p>Customers can use any of the latest generation smart phones, including iPhone, Windows Mobile, Android, Palm and Blackberry phones, to access their dashboard.<br />
      </p>
    </div>
